  ('27e371d2-2dcb-428c-a32a-a17e246f02e8', 'Casaba Outlet', 'APLL', NULL),
  ('db2fdcd3-aa45-4878-bdba-8d6062885f45', 'Casaba Outlet', 'ATRO', NULL),
  ('4f6dafd0-0b7e-4aac-844a-356896049adc', 'Casaba Outlet', 'TDD', NULL),
  ('d73a45ce-6b59-4791-937d-1bd7a0819ee0', 'Casaba Outlet', 'CUBY', NULL),
  ('435366d8-8b47-4cbc-b0cf-688a95a0847d', 'Yorm', 'YORM', 'Gotlieb Yorm was a top racing pilot on the professional circuit, who was known for his willingness to do anything to shave a few more seconds off his lap times. For a short while, before the Safety Commission stepped in, he would race naked, claiming clothes were an unnecessary weight. Another such innovation that was considerably more successful (and modest) was his insistence that the shields being used on his racer were too powerful. He really only needed to be able to fend off a few shots, because after that he would either have maneuvered his ship out of targeting range, or he would have lost the race anyway. Gutting apart an existing shield by hand, Yorm hacked together a lighter shield that would draw less power and only protect him just enough to escape. Soon, many other racers were trying to mimic his efforts, and when Yorm retired, he went on to successfully sell his modified shield design.'),
  ('9e1f5a35-edcc-4d19-bede-08e2730043c5', 'Argo Astronautics', 'ARGO', 'This commercial ship manufacturer focuses on building shuttles, transport vessels and utility vehicles that can be seen around the universe.'),
  ('4835d29c-3cdd-4983-97b2-1af4674c4c00', 'Sakura Sun', 'ROO', 'Soft drinks, high end kitchen equipment, children’s toys? Sakura Sun. Rover platforms, terraforming solutions, bioengineered livestock? Sakura Sun. High-tech wave cannons, starship power plants, antimatter ordinance? Sakura Sun! While corporate conglomerates are not uncommon, it’s rare for any company to advertise them all under the same banner. But at Sakura Sun, empire-building is in full effect: you’ll find a little bit of everything branded with a distinctive purple sun-and-cherry-blossom logo, from plastic Hi-Ho Flatcat figurines to top-of-the-line multi-particle/wave cannons. Stranger still, Sakura Sun has successfully gained a reputation as a company that not only does a little bit of everything, but does it well.'),
  ('ad865899-f5ba-4818-ae8c-fe80a55108b7', 'Broad & Rabiee', 'BRRA', 'Founded by a pair of aerospace engineers, Broad & Rabiee began with a line of computers and components before branching out to turrets.'),
  ('60d0f346-0c22-4869-81d3-1168b526a258', 'Lightning Power Ltd.', 'LPLT', 'Made out of less expensive materials, Lightning Power continues to introduce new aesthetic changes to their ship components while relying on tried and true technology to run them.'),
  ('bcea197e-ac9d-49f4-a692-d77c6927077f', 'Blue Triangle Inc.', 'BLTR', 'Makers of advanced computer and analytic systems, Blue Triangle prides itself on hiring only the best engineers and programmers, many of whom started their careers as black hat hackers.'),
  ('a349d45f-cda5-4fdb-89ea-4ea91804a163', 'Kilgore and Poole', 'KAP', 'Kilgore and Poole caters its armor and image to a high-end clientele. Criticized by some as prioritizing form over function, their eye-catching armor favors ease of movement and agility over heavy defense.'),
  ('b9b97673-c585-4e0a-b229-a0a3c79668c3', 'Flashfire Systems', 'FFSY', 'Failed laser weapon manufacturer. Transformed into an engineering firm that came up with the weapon mount system that''s almost uniformly used.'),
  ('d1a1bf03-89d9-4eae-ac34-11eeb8e45d8f', 'Thermyte Concern', 'THCN', 'Thermyte Concern'),
  ('cfc0122d-5275-415a-a656-3dcb3346feb5', 'Ace Astrogation', 'ACAS', 'Corp focusing on the structural (non-combat) aspects of the ship. Builds sleek, elegant but powerful power plants.'),
  ('de0d3594-9f18-42c0-8a90-6edd723d80f8', 'Aegis Dynamics', 'MXOX', 'Aegis grew to prominence as a manufacturer of military spacecraft during the First Tevarin War. Favored by Ivar Messer, their orbital bombers grew to public prominence after his infamous victory on Idris IV and became synonymous with the ruthless Messer regime that followed. After the Fall of the Imperator, Aegis'' contracts were stripped, their ships fell out of favor with the public, and the company went into a tailspin. They downsized their craft production and turned to manufacturing parts. However, time heals all wounds and today Aegis has risen once again to be a top military contractor of ships and components.'),
  ('7b4402a1-f17f-4125-afcc-4a159dcd29e0', 'KnightBridge Arms', 'KBAR', 'Headquartered in the Kiel system, KnightBridge Arms is there to protect you and yours. With a weapon for every price point, you can rest assured that KnightBridge has your back.'),
  ('a2a97679-2a6e-4e89-80d8-439c88a01427', 'Tyler Design & Tech', 'TYDT', 'Tyler Design & Tech began its life manufacturing generators, air purifiers, and other necessities for planetary settlers. Tyler focused on making products that, while not as powerful as some other brands, were durable and extremely efficient with little heat byproduct which led to the development of low-signature power plants.  It wasn’t long before even the UEE Navy began to outfit some of their own stealth crafts with Tyler parts, and with their new success the company was able to expand their ship component line into what it is today.'),
  ('06370f79-4741-4781-be08-d5acc9e28047', 'Aopoa', 'XNAA', 'Though many attributed their elevation to the sole provider of light craft to audacity and daring, Aopoa cemented their position thanks to the innovative dual-vector thruster technology that has revolutionized their ship design.'),
  ('5f81335d-44e6-4104-841e-c5af9df06829', 'Aegis Dynamics', 'FSKI', 'Aegis grew to prominence as a manufacturer of military spacecraft during the First Tevarin War. Favored by Ivar Messer, their orbital bombers grew to public prominence after his infamous victory on Idris IV and became synonymous with the ruthless Messer regime that followed. After the Fall of the Imperator, Aegis'' contracts were stripped, their ships fell out of favor with the public, and the company went into a tailspin. They downsized their craft production and turned to manufacturing parts. However, time heals all wounds and today Aegis has risen once again to be a top military contractor of ships and components.'),
  ('eccba58a-f6d9-42e8-95c6-d0a65763e583', 'Amon & Reese Co.', 'AMRS', 'Formed early in the Messer era by recent veterans Marcelo Amon and Travis Reese, A&R Co. is one of the oldest energy weapon manufacturers in the UEE. Their designs have always been user focused and they have a well-earned reputation for dependability and ease of use, something the company claims derives from a dedication to field testing that well exceeds what other companies do.'),
  ('d8ef0f35-e196-4d18-affa-750f6cdf8cb4', 'Wen/Cassel Propulsion', 'WCPR', 'Subsidiary of RSI, handles a small percentage of their thruster and ship options construction as well as cooling systems.'),
  ('b922abdb-0634-4358-9eee-60118f3cf3a7', 'Anvil Aerospace', 'ANVL', 'For civilians, Anvil Aerospace produces small fighting craft but with less of the pirate stigma. These ships are more expensive, less spit-and-glue, and built to take more hits than a comparable Drake model. The bulk of Anvil''s income is from its military contracts with the UEE to design and build their warships, especially the iconic Hornet.'),
  ('b28a5c61-63a4-478b-8047-5fba545d5b8a', 'Musashi Industrial & Starflight Concern', 'MIS', 'Mass produces very efficient, modular ships, mostly armored freighters of different sizes that make them the preferred brand for traders and larger corporations. Over thirty years ago, MISC signed a lend-lease agreement to establish a tech trade with Xi’An engineers.'),
  ('0d3e6377-4be0-4c38-8269-3ac5dbd132d8', 'Syang Fabrication', 'SYFB', 'PH Syang Fabrication Description'),
  ('73a6ba90-8f53-423d-ad0b-96e81b7e18a5', 'Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems', 'RRS', 'Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems (RRS) is an Earth-based corporation that provides rehabilitation services, personal body armor and defensive systems throughout the UEE. Their arms division is responsible for a groundbreaking series of new weaponry designed to incapacitate opponents without taking lives.'),
  ('8a7bd715-5b97-404f-b02e-0d0cc593f608', 'Clark Defense Systems', 'CDS', 'Ground-combat defensive systems, covers a lot of commercial territory from personal armor to defense systems. Naming convention tend to be pretty straight-forward and logical.

Models: PAB-4 (Personal Ablative/Ballistic Light Armor)

QDB-12 QuiKCade (Quick Deployment Barricade)'),
  ('d133f90d-bc69-4273-9867-6c03631f0c4b', 'UEE Navy', 'NVY', '(PH) UEE Navy - Description'),
  ('be4a26fd-0585-4aaf-bad9-d234091bd02e', 'CC''s Conversions', 'CCC', 'CC''s Conversions Description'),
  ('eddc1a94-7840-4855-9889-544821d4d739', 'Caldera', 'CLDA', 'Caldera Description.'),
  ('b495993e-c10a-41e4-876d-1de96de54e33', 'Doomsday', 'DOOM', 'Extremely aggressive looking homemade armor meant to protect and intimidate. This kind of armor is not only expected to survive the apocalypse, but also dominate its aftermath.'),
  ('0e6d8f1b-ebb8-4773-8ca4-f25d737c8709', 'Virgil', 'VGL', 'High-end Commercial and Personal armor manufacturer. Aside from combat uses, they build systems for heavy commercial and mining applications.

Models: Achilles PDS (Heavy Combat Armor)

Zeus System (Titan Armor)'),
  ('8368a760-84b4-4359-bda1-7b015dc0c884', 'Hardin Tactical', 'HDTC', 'PH Hardin Tactical Desc'),
  ('04ded06f-7862-4771-b40f-aa310b74ee17', 'Universal Body Armor', 'UBA', '- Universal Body Armor Description'),
  ('c0bc7b2d-9c1a-4029-9715-f28b81122863', 'Tehachapi', 'THP', 'PH - Tehachapi Description'),
  ('709e8255-a0b1-4c5e-8b0e-28781be25984', 'Kastak Arms', 'KSAR', 'Kastak Arms makes inexpensive energy weapons with intimidating names like Devastator and Firestorm, and aggressively markets them to distressed parts of the Empire. Even though the company portrays itself as providing weapons for personal defense, the brand has become more readily identified with people who use them for aggressive and unlawful purposes.'),
  ('093e6eba-93fa-4dad-b3dd-38966934e34e', 'Roberts Space Industries', 'RSI', 'The original creators of the engine that kickstarted Humanity’s expansion into space, Roberts Space Industries builds a wide range of spaceships that serve all needs, from basic interstellar travel to deep exploration on the outer edges of the galaxy. The tagline is “Roberts Space Industries: Delivering the Stars since 2075”'),
  ('9f0f7735-d389-4c7d-95f1-c4d0c57f7214', 'microTech', 'MIT', 'Ubiquitous around the Empire, microTech and their range of electronics, datapads, mobile interfaces, handheld sensors and computer software upgrades for starships are used daily by almost everyone. Their line of mobiGlas personal computers have become an integral part of daily life for millions of people.'),
  ('819545f4-18af-49a6-814e-ca4fd08f56e5', 'Greycat Industrial', 'GRIN', 'A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.'),
  ('63685f47-b0cc-4ebe-8f16-72793a5cd6e0', 'Crusader Industries', 'CRUS', 'Makers of an extensive fleet of cargo, vehicle and data transport ships, and cutting edge shuttles, Crusader Industries is a titan of the aerospace industry. It is a company so powerful and prominent that it purchased a gas giant in the Stanton system to house its current headquarters.'),
  ('d8eca6d3-b40c-46c0-953e-ef5840c1fa63', 'Greycat Industrial', 'GRIN', 'A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.'),
  ('abca0ae0-a819-4aeb-a1a7-f8f1d7e277cf', 'Ascension Astro', 'ASAS', 'Ascension Astro started off as a boutique specialty company; selling high-end, low IR thrusters to wealthy clients who wanted to fly their luxury ships while avoiding the eyes of greedy pirates. As good as their thrusters were at being low-sig, the effect was often ruined when the engines or shielding made by other manufacturers would be screaming the ship’s presence. Slowly, Ascension began expanding their line to include a whole suite of components that, when working in conjunction, would provide an extremely low profile and a safer journey.'),
  ('768b4380-6486-4187-8c22-bc3deaf80770', 'Grey''s Market', 'GLSN', 'A fleet of mobile marketplaces that caters to high-end clients interested in experiencing the wild side of the ''verse to gain access to unusual and unique items.'),
  ('055fe7c5-2e02-4e3a-aacb-f289563fabbd', 'PH Associated Science and Development', 'ASD', 'PH Associated Science and Development Description'),
  ('0f9ffe57-8542-4d83-a246-72568a5f2f91', 'Wei-Tek', 'WETK', 'Upstart company made by former employees of Ascension Astro.'),
  ('57bfcf3d-13f6-4c2c-b7c7-6bf8eacb8a24', 'Gorgon Defender Industries', 'GODI', 'When Humanity started being attacked by Vanduul, it was often those who lived in the border system who suffered the most. Believing that civilian defensive components were not up to facing this deadly enemy, Gorgon Defender Industries, founded by former inhabitants of Caliban, was established to take military strength products and deliver it the population at large so they could properly protect themselves. With the strength of their designs, Gorgon earned a reputation that soon caught the eye of the military.'),
  ('2e06e775-940b-4c24-8974-31fb5617ea56', 'United Empire of Earth', 'UEE', 'The unified collection of planets and systems under Human control, the UEE strives to create a safe and just empire, championing equality and opportunity for all its inhabitants.'),
  ('8af71a8a-7da0-4e31-afc7-648fc916e387', 'Chimera Communications', 'CHCO', 'A dedicated manufacturer of communication, radar and scan systems. They are the rugged go-to company for miners and explorers alike with their sturdy, well-tested and dependable products.'),
  ('2b25a2dd-47ea-4ab0-8711-03d34be214b1', 'Tarsus', 'TARS', 'Founded by a pair of mechanics who were attempting to make an affordable module that would convert a quantum drive into a jump drive, Tarsus has evolved to become one of the main producers of dependable jump drives in the UEE. Over time they also expanded to build their own quantum drives as well.'),
  ('dd55bc19-5212-4365-bbc8-73474f0257ed', 'Curelife', 'CUR', 'Makes medical packs for commercial purposes. Formed by a group of doctors, CureLife was the first company to offer heavy medical solutions to the general public.'),
  ('bb5a8287-6bb7-4936-a898-4b1850e8112e', 'PH Associated Science and Development', 'ASD', 'PH Associated Science and Development Description'),
  ('f80ab8de-4d04-4a1f-a8f2-ee2bb01fd125', 'Consumable', 'GEND', 'PH Generic Drink Description'),
  ('ab35f85f-919f-4457-8d58-4e885ea6c5c0', 'Shubin Interstellar', 'SHIN', 'Shubin Interstellar Description'),
  ('1b6be99e-f430-459f-ab2a-a912fd6722f8', 'Consumable', 'GENF', 'PH Generic Food Description'),
  ('57432775-b421-45cc-8616-ac2d35018193', 'RAMP Corporation', 'RACO', 'Manufacturer of consumer and pro-grade ship components, RAMP Corp sponsors the Team RAMP M50 racing team.'),
  ('67fd3077-ee8c-4a7c-8bad-91500b2a9509', 'Nova Pyrotechnica', 'NOVP', 'An company out of Terra that offers missiles and rockets at a low price.'),
  ('2a64f92e-8f6d-47ac-a6ed-643465e91d4b', 'Kroneg', 'KRON', 'Kroneg Description'),
  ('77f7999a-b23b-4812-94c2-09b5e15e1b0e', 'Apocalypse Arms', 'APAR', 'Apocalypse Arms produces aggressive, devastating weapons inspired by Messer-Era technology.'),
  ('6116471c-891d-4830-8968-650b6deafc00', 'Drake Interplanetary', 'DRAK', 'Makes affordable, modular ships that have become the go-to manufacturer for anyone looking to get their first ship, but have become associated with criminal elements.')
on conflict (id) do nothing;

-- 137 fabricantes.